text: Kogane, did you bring your lunch?

Yeah, I'm fine today!
I won't make the same mistake again!!!

I just thought about what happened last time
and... It just slipped out...

Sakuya~! Let's all have lunch together next time!
Think about what you want to eat~!

Yeah, I'm really looking forward to it.
Take care!

Wait for me, Kogatan── Oh, Sakuyan!
Did Kogatan already leave?!

Yeah── I think she just left,
so she might still be under the stairs.

That's a relief!
She forgot her lunch again...!

──Alright, I'll make sure to bring it on time this time.
And Meguru, you're going straight to your lesson!

Haha, have a good time.
I hope your lesson goes well!

Leave it to me! We'll show off the results
of our fun dancing at the group rehearsal!
Being busy is a good thing...

Hi there! Mamimi, Kiriko. Hehe, thanks to
you two for coming early, I got to see you both.

Hehe...
What's that supposed to mean?
